      "content": "but it's not just about \"moving on\" to a new chapter. how do you even do that when you have nothing left? no money, no career, no sense of who you even are without the research. i'm just so exhausted. i feel like i've been running a marathon for years and i just hit a wall that isn't going to move. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to rest.",
